        <item>
            <title>Apple 擴展自助維修計劃，提供遠程維修判斷</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/apple-diagnostics-for-self-service-repair/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-diagnostics-for-self-service-repair</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/apple-diagnostics-for-self-service-repair/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 03:07:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Diagnostics for Self Service Repair]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210498</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 宣佈擴大其自助維修計劃，允許 iPhone 15 用户和新款 M2 MacBook 用户自行維修設備。現在可以自己維修設備，該計劃正擴展到另外 24 個歐洲國家。但也許更有趣的是 「Apple Diagnostics for Self Service Repair」的發佈，Apple 稱它將幫助自助維修者「測試設備的最佳部件功能和性能，並確定哪些部件可能需要維修」。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210499 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-1.22.49-PM-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-1.22.49-PM-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-1.22.49-PM-1280x851.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-1.22.49-PM-768x511.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-1.22.49-PM-1536x1021.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-14-at-1.22.49-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple Diagnostics for Self Service Repair</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">這款基於網路的診斷工具目前已在美國上市，用户將需要排除故障的設備調到診斷模式，將其序號輸入輔助設備，然後按照 Apple 的説明對損壞的設備進行故障排除。 可用的測試包括檢查設備的硬體和軟體版本，確定顯示器問題（包括像素異常和多點觸控問題）、相機、Face ID 和音訊輸出。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">在發布該工具的同時，蘋果也將自助維修服務擴展到更多的 iPhone 和 Mac，包括更多基於 M2 的機型。 在 6 月擴大自助服務維修計畫時，只包括 13 吋 M2 MacBook Air 和 MacBook Pro。 而現時，該計劃涵蓋了多種 M2 電腦，包括 14 吋和 16 吋 MacBook Pro、15 吋 MacBook Air、Mac Mini、Mac Pro 和 Mac Studio。Apple 指，該計劃目前已在 33 個國家使用，使用 24 種語言，可用於維修 35 種產品。 Apple Diagnostics for Self Service Repair 目前只在美國提供，明年將擴展到歐洲。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/13/23999669/apple-self-service-repair-diagnostics-m2-macbook-iphone-15">The Verge</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/apple-diagnostics-for-self-service-repair/fun-tech/">Apple 擴展自助維修計劃，提供遠程維修判斷</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/apple-diagnostics-for-self-service-repair/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本麥當勞推出「薯條加濕器」 散發薯條香氣</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mcdonaldsjapan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 03:07:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[買物情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[日本麥當勞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[薯條加濕器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[麥當勞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210096</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">日本麥當勞推出 2024 年福袋，當中最觸目是號稱使用後可令房間充滿薯條味的「薯條加濕器」。消息推出後，即時引來網民討論。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">2024 年の福袋は「BRUNO」とコラボ🐧✨<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%83%9E%E3%82%AF%E3%83%89%E3%83%8A%E3%83%AB%E3%83%89%E3%81%AE%E7%A6%8F%E8%A2%8B2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#マクドナルドの福袋 2024</a> 事前抽選販売応募受付中❗<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BRUNO%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E3%82%B3%E3%83%A9%E3%83%9C%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BRUNO 限定コラボアイテム</a> と <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E7%84%A1%E6%96%99%E5%88%B8?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#商品無料券</a> をゲットしよう❗</p><p>チャーミングな「ポテト加濕器」や、BRUNOならではのおしゃれなアイテムがたくさん❗<br />さらに10 人に1 人、金のマックカードが當たるチャンスも❗</p><p>&mdash; マクドナルド (@McDonaldsJapan) <a href="https://twitter.com/McDonaldsJapan/status/1734400176943440287?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 12, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">是次推出的麥當勞 2024 年福袋是與日本生活品牌 BRUNO 聯名合作，加濕器外型是經典的紅色包裝和金黃薯條，其中一個賣點是加濕器會散發薯條香氣。要獲得薯條加濕器，需要在 12 月 19 日前，在日本 McDonald’s App 申請抽獎資格。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210100 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/05-8.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/05-8.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/05-8-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲薯條加濕器</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了薯條加濕器外，福袋裏還有毯子、零錢包、迷你盤子及大量餐點免費兑換券，包括武士漢堡（炙燒醬油雙層牛肉）、照燒漢堡、蘋果派、OREO 巧克力冰沙、研磨咖啡等，總價值高達 3,430 日圓。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210104 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/09.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/09.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/09-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲毯子</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210101 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/07.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/07.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/07-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲零錢包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1210103 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/08.png" alt="" width="490" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/08.png 490w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/08-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲迷你盤子</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.mcdonalds.co.jp/campaign/lb-2024-r57a0/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=cpe&amp;utm_campaign=luckybag-2024&amp;utm_term=promo-tweet&amp;af_prt=dentsudigital">McDonaldsJapan</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/">日本麥當勞推出「薯條加濕器」 散發薯條香氣</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/17/mcdonaldsjapan/shop_guide/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
